content.text:
Perfect! Now I have all the information. Let me create a comprehensive report of the signup, login, and auth modal design.

---

## COMPREHENSIVE AUTH PAGES ANALYSIS

### DESIGN SYSTEM OVERVIEW

**Color Palette (from `index.css`):**
- **Primary Background:** `#FAF9F6` (warm cream) / Dark: `#0C0C0C`
- **Accent Gold:** `#D4A853` (amber)
- **Text Primary:** `#1A1612` (very dark brown) / Dark: `#F0EBE3`
- **Text Heading:** `#12100D`
- **Text Body:** `#8A8480` (warm gray-brown)
- **Text Muted:** `#A8A29E`
- **Error Red:** `#DC2626`
- **Success Green:** `#16A34A`

**Typography:**
- **Serif:** Lora (body copy, italic subtitles)
- **Display/Brand:** Playfair Display (uppercase, serif)
- **UI/Form:** Lexend Deca or Outfit (sans-serif)

---

## 1. SIGNUP PAGE (`signup.jsx` + `signup.css`)

### JSX Structure
```
<div class="auth-shell signup-shell">
  ├── <section class="auth-panel">
  │   ├── <div class="brand">Iskrib</div> (with ::after line)
  │   ├── <h1 class="panel-title">Create your quiet writing space.</h1>
  │   ├── <p class="panel-copy">Keep your poems, journals, and reflections beautifully organized.</p>
  │   └── <div class="panel-details">Private drafts · Elegant publishing · Calm community</div>
  │
  └── <section class="auth-form-panel">
      └── <div class="auth-form-card">
          ├── <div>
          │   ├── <div class="form-title">Create an account</div>
          │   └── <p class="form-subtitle">Start writing in minutes.</p>
          │
          ├── <form class="auth-form">
          │   ├── <div class="form-field"> (Email)
          │   │   ├── <label>Email</label>
          │   │   └── <div class="input-with-action">
          │   │       ├── <input id="signup-email" type="email" placeholder="you@iskrib.com" />
          │   │       └── <div class="length-counter">{email.length}/50</div>
          │   │
          │   ├── <div class="form-field"> (Password)
          │   │   ├── <label>Password</label>
          │   │   └── <div class="input-with-action">
          │   │       ├── <input id="signup-password" type="password|text" placeholder="Create a password" />
          │   │       └── <button class="show-toggle">Show/Hide</button>
          │   │
          │   ├── <div class="captcha-container">
          │   │   └── <Turnstile /> (Cloudflare CAPTCHA widget)
          │   │
          │   ├── <button class="primary-button" type="submit">
          │   │   ├── <span class="button-label">Create account</span>
          │   │   └── <span class="button-spinner" /> (animated on loading)
          │   │
          │   └── <button class="secondary-button" type="button" onClick={() => navigate('/home')}>
          │       Explore Iskrib
          │
          ├── <div class="auth-footer">
          │   ├── Have an account?
          │   └── <button class="link-button">Log in</button>
          │
          └── {errorMessage && <div class="form-message error">{errorMessage}</div>}
          └── {successMessage && <div class="form-message success">{successMessage}</div>}
```

### Form Validation & State Management
- **Email:** Regex validation `/^[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+$/`
- **Password:** Required (no specific strength rules shown)
- **CAPTCHA:** Cloudflare Turnstile (required before submit)
- **Disable Submit:** If email/password/captcha missing OR loading
- **Success Flow:** Email sent → 600ms delay → redirect to `/home`
- **Error Display:** Role="alert" for accessibility

### CSS Styling Details

**Left Panel (Brand Story):**
```css
.auth-panel {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  padding: 64px 72px;
  background: var(--bg-card); /* #FEFEFE */
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border-card);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
```

**Decorative Morphing Blobs (Ink/Watercolor effect):**
```css
.auth-panel::before {
  content: '';
  width: 400px; height: 400px;
  border-radius: 47% 53% 61% 39% / 45% 51% 49% 55%;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 30%, 
              rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.08), 
              transparent 70%);
  animation: morph 20s ease-in-out infinite;
  position: absolute; top: -120px; left: -100px;
}

@keyframes morph {
  0%, 100% { border-radius: 47% 53% 61% 39% / 45% 51% 49% 55%; }
  25% { border-radius: 55% 45% 50% 50% / 60% 40% 60% 40%; }
  50% { border-radius: 40% 60% 55% 45% / 50% 55% 45% 50%; }
  75% { border-radius: 60% 40% 45% 55% / 45% 60% 40% 55%; }
}
```

**Brand Logo:**
```css
.brand {
  font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
  font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent-amber); /* #D4A853 */
  margin-bottom: 48px;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}

.brand::after {
  content: '';
  display: block;
  width: 32px; height: 2px;
  background: var(--accent-amber);
  margin-top: 16px;
  opacity: 0.5;
}
```

**Panel Title & Copy:**
```css
.panel-title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif); /* Lora */
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
  font-weight: 500; font-style: italic;
  line-height: 1.25;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--text-heading);
}

.panel-copy {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: var(--text-body);
  line-height: 1.75;
}
```

**Form Card (Right Panel):**
```css
.auth-form-card {
  max-width: 400px;
  padding: 40px 36px;
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-card); /* rgba(120,100,80,0.08) */
  border-radius: 12px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-sm); /* 0 1px 2px rgba(80,60,40,0.05) */
  animation: slideUp 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) both;
}

@keyframes slideUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
```

**Form Inputs:**
```css
.auth-input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-card);
  background: var(--bg-primary);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
}

.auth-input:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-light);
}

.auth-input:focus {
  outline: none;
  border-color: var(--accent-amber);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.12); /* Gold glow */
  background: var(--bg-primary);
}

.auth-input::placeholder {
  color: var(--text-faint);
  font-style: italic;
}
```

**Show/Hide Password Toggle:**
```css
.show-toggle {
  position: absolute; right: 12px;
  background: var(--bg-pill); /* rgba(120,100,80,0.06) */
  border: none;
  font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  padding: 6px 10px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
}

.show-toggle:hover {
  background: var(--bg-hover);
  color: var(--accent-amber);
}

.input-with-action .auth-input {
  padding-right: 72px;
}
```

**Buttons:**
```css
/* Primary Button (Dark/Black) */
.primary-button {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 14px 20px;
  background: var(--text-heading); /* #12100D */
  color: var(--bg-primary); /* #FAF9F6 */
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}

.primary-button:hover:not(:disabled) {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
}

.primary-button:disabled {
  opacity: 0.5;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}

/* Secondary Button (Outlined) */
.secondary-button {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 13px 18px;
  background: transparent;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-card);
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
}

.secondary-button:hover:not(:disabled) {
  border-color: var(--accent-amber);
  background: rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.04);
  color: var(--accent-amber);
}
```

**Loading Spinner:**
```css
.button-spinner {
  width: 14px; height: 14px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  border-top-color: #fff;
  animation: spin 0.7s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes spin {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}
```

**Messages (Error/Success):**
```css
.form-message {
  padding: 12px 14px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
}

.form-message.error {
  background: var(--color-danger-bg); /* rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.08) */
  color: var(--color-danger); /* #DC2626 */
  border-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);
}

.form-message.success {
  background: var(--color-success-bg); /* rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.08) */
  color: var(--color-success); /* #16A34A */
  border-color: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.2);
}
```

**Length Counter (Email):**
```css
.length-counter {
  position: absolute; right: 12px; top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* Turns red at 50 characters */
```

**Link Button (Footer):**
```css
.link-button {
  background: none; border: none;
  color: var(--accent-amber);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 0;
  transition: color 0.15s ease;
}

.link-button:hover {
  color: var(--text-heading);
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-underline-offset: 3px;
}

.link-button:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--accent-amber);
  outline-offset: 2px;
  border-radius: 4px;
}
```

### Responsive Behavior

**Desktop (1024px+):** Two-column split layout (brand left, form right)

**Tablet (max-width: 1024px):**
```css
/* Stacks vertically */
.auth-shell { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.auth-panel { flex-shrink: 0; padding: 48px 40px; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid... }
.auth-form-card { max-width: 100%; box-shadow: none; background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; }
```

**Mobile (max-width: 600px):**
- Font sizes reduce (title: 1.65rem)
- Form inputs: `font-size: 16px` (prevents iOS zoom)
- Padding: 36px 24px on panel, 32px 20px on form
- Panel details wrap with `flex-wrap: wrap`

**Accessibility (prefers-reduced-motion):**
- All animations disabled
- Transitions removed

### Dark Mode
- Primary button becomes gold: `background: var(--accent-amber);` + `color: #1A1612;`
- Enhanced shadow on hover: `0 4px 20px rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.25)`
- Blobs fade: opacity reduced from 0.08 to 0.06/0.04

---

## 2. LOGIN PAGE (`login.jsx` + `login.css`)

### JSX Structure (Nearly Identical to Signup)
```
<div class="auth-shell login-shell">
  ├── <section class="auth-panel">
  │   ├── <div class="brand">Iskrib</div>
  │   ├── <h1 class="panel-title">A calm place to write, reflect, and share.</h1>
  │   ├── <p class="panel-copy">Keep your thoughts in one quiet space. Publish when you are ready.</p>
  │   └── <div class="panel-details">Minimalist editor · Private drafts · Thoughtful community</div>
  │
  └── <section class="auth-form-panel">
      └── <div class="auth-form-card">
          ├── <header>
          │   ├── <h2 class="form-title">
          │   │   {forgotMode ? 'Reset your password' : 'Welcome back'}
          │   └── <p class="form-subtitle">
          │       {forgotMode ? "Enter your email..." : "Sign in to continue..."}
          │
          ├── {forgotMode ? (
          │   <form class="auth-form">
          │     ├── <div class="form-field"> (Email only)
