}
```

**Mobile Responsiveness (max-width: 480px):**
```css
.auth-modal-container {
  width: 85%;
  padding: 1.5rem;
}
```

---

## VISUAL "FEEL" & DESIGN LANGUAGE

**Overall Aesthetic:**
- **Editorial/Literary** — inspired by Medium, Substack, book publishing
- **Minimalist & Calm** — maximum negative space, gentle typography
- **Warm, Organic** — earthy color palette (browns, golds, warm grays)
- **Refined Elegance** — serif typeface for headlines, careful letter-spacing
- **Subtle Animation** — morph blobs, slide-up cards, spring entrances (not jarring)

**Key Design Principles:**

1. **Typography Hierarchy:**
   - Brand: Playfair Display (uppercase, spaced)
   - Headlines: Playfair Display (serif, italic)
   - Body: Lora (serif, warm)
   - UI: Lexend Deca/Outfit (clean, sans-serif)

2. **Color Strategy:**
   - Monochromatic dark/light with gold accents
   - Emphasis through opacity rather than bright colors
   - Soft shadows (no harsh drop-shadows)
   - Glass morphism elements (subtle blur, low opacity)

3. **Spacing:**
   - Generous padding (40px form cards, 64px brand panels)
   - Breathing room between form fields (gap: 20px)
   - Vertical rhythm maintained (multiples of 8px)

4. **Interactive Elements:**
   - **Inputs:** Amber glow on focus, smooth transitions
   - **Buttons:** Subtle lift on hover (translateY: -1px), shadow increase
   - **Links:** Amber text, underline on hover
   - **Toggles:** Pill-shaped, muted by default

5. **Decorative Elements:**
   - Morphing blobs (organic, liquid feel)
   - Thin gold underline under brand
   - Decorative dots in feature list

6. **Accessibility:**
   - All interactive elements are clearly labeled
   - Focus states are visible (outline or box-shadow)
   - Reduced motion support (animations disabled)
   - ARIA attributes (role="alert", aria-busy, etc.)

7. **Dark Mode:**
   - Inverts colors while maintaining warmth
   - Gold becomes brighter (#E0BA6A)
   - Text becomes light (#F0EBE3)
   - Blobs fade further (more subtle)
   - Button hover shadows enhanced for contrast

---

## THIRD-PARTY LIBRARIES USED

1. **Framer Motion** — AnimatePresence, motion.div, spring/tween animations
2. **React Router** — useNavigate for page transitions
3. **Supabase Auth** — signUp, signInWithPassword, resetPasswordForEmail
4. **Cloudflare Turnstile** — CAPTCHA widget (signup page only)

---

## RESPONSIVE STRATEGY

| Breakpoint | Layout | Changes |
|-----------|--------|---------|
| **1024px+** | 2-column grid (left panel 1fr, right form 1fr) | Full-size brand story visible |
| **1024px** | Flex column (stacks vertically) | Form card loses shadow, becomes borderless |
| **600px-1024px** | Single column | Padding reduced, fonts scale down |
| **<600px** | Single column + full width | Modal width: 85%, font-size: 16px on inputs |

---

## ERROR & SUCCESS MESSAGE STATES

| State | Background | Text Color | Border | Animation |
